data.description: Come see this beautifully updated home featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an open floor plan.  Once inside, you are invited by the first living area with great natural lighting and an open concept with a dining area and a kitchen that boasts granite countertops, a stainless steel stove, pantry, and island.  Make your way to the second living area that is spacious and has a fireplace. The primary suite features two closets, its own access to the backyard, and an ensuite with dual sinks. Finally, step outside to the covered patio and a backyard with additional concrete areas and a storage shed. Other great features include ceiling fans throughout, an HVAC unit that was replaced in 2020, and artificial grass in the front yard. Call and schedule your tour today.
